These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, drawing
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, canadian
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Hobby   | sudoku  | drawing |
| Nationality     | canadian | argentine  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, march
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Birthday    | august      | march         |
| Beverage   | 7up | cola |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, country
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, horror
1. the fan of folk is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | country | folk   |
| Movie-Genre       | horror  | animation |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea  | hot-chocolate |
| Pet         | chinchilla | horse    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, snowboarding
The people have 2 different jobs:  engineer, fisherman
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |
| Sport      | water-polo | snowboarding |
| Job   | fisherman        | engineer  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-6::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, oliveros
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, writer
1. the writer is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |
| Cigar        | oliveros  | fonseca |
| Job   | coach | writer  |

