.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-8::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, bike
2 different pets are kept: turtle, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |
| Transport   | bike     | subway   |
| Pet        | turtle | mouse |

